`returnScope` has the following syntax in your queries:**Search:**$search Syntax```json
{
  $search: {
   "<operator>": {
      <operator-specification>,
   },
   "returnScope": {
      "path": "<embedded-documents-field-to-retrieve>"
   },
   "returnStoredSource": true
  }
}
```**Search-meta:**$searchMeta Syntax```json
{
  $searchMeta: {
   "returnScope": {
      "path": "<embedded-documents-field-to-retrieve>"
   },
   "returnStoredSource": true
  },
  "facet": {
    "<operator>": {
      <operator-specification>,
   },
    "facets": {
      <facet-definition>
    }
  }
}
```To learn more about query syntax, see [$search](pipe.$search).
